---
title: Saucy Barbecue Chicken with a Creamy Green Bean and Potato Salad
description: With temperatures rising, we’re getting in the mood for some more summery fare. To scratch that itch, we’re turning to a favorite: barbecue chicken. There are few dishes that suggest food, fun, and festiveness quite like white meat dripping with a sweet and tangy sauce. And because there’s no need to mess with a classic, we’re adding a traditional creamy potato salad with green beans on the side.
